*Purpose:   TypeScript compiler configuration for the project.
*           Defines compiler options, module resolution,
*           path aliases, and included/excluded files.
*Revisions:
*v1.0 - 18-09-2025 - Initial configuration
*v1.2 - 16-10-2025 - Add baseUrl
